      <title>软银和东京电子的盈利有望因人工智能芯片需求而得到提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/softbank-tokyo-electron-get-ai-support-global-chip-wars-may-buoy-japan-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东京电子有限公司 (Tokyo Electron Ltd.) 和 Lasertec Corp. 将紧随芯片巨头 SK 海力士公司 (SK Hynix Inc.) 和三星电子公司 (Samsung Electronics Co.) 之后公布业绩，这两家公司受益于人工智能使用的高带宽内存芯片的强劲需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/softbank-tokyo-electron-get-ai-support-global-chip-wars-may-buoy-japan-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大多数日本央行观察人士重新考虑加息步伐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/most-bank-of-japan-watchers-rethink-pace-of-interest-rate-hikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在央行行长上田一夫发表强硬言论并提前加息后，大多数日本央行观察人士都在重新评估利率走势并提前预测。布莱恩·福勒在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/most-bank-of-japan-watchers-rethink-pace-of-interest-rate-hikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 01:12:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三星成为人工智能关注焦点，亚洲芯片股领头羊发生变动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/asian-chip-stock-leadership-shifts-as-samsung-grabs-ai-spotlight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲芯片股的领导地位正在发生变化，在寻找人工智能行业下一个佼佼者的过程中，外国投资者的买入推动了三星电子公司的股价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/asian-chip-stock-leadership-shifts-as-samsung-grabs-ai-spotlight</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 00:58:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>权力平衡 08/01/24</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/balance-of-power-08-01-24</link>
      <description><![CDATA[“权力平衡”关注政治与全球商业的交汇。今天，密歇根州民主党众议员 Haley Stevens 和《华尔街日报》助理编辑 Paul Beckett 就俄罗斯释放美国记者这一美国、俄罗斯和其他国家之间重大囚犯交换事件进行了讨论。雪城大学政治学教授 Jenn Jackson 和爱荷华州共和党众议员 Ashley Hinson 在芝加哥举行的全国黑人记者协会大会上分享了他们对前总统特朗普言论的看法。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/balance-of-power-08-01-24</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 00:57:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美国就业数据公布，美国国债涨势延续至第七天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/treasury-two-year-yields-fall-to-14-month-low-on-fed-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债价格连续第七天上涨，因为交易员关注即将发布的就业数据，以巩固他们的观点，即美国将在9月份降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/treasury-two-year-yields-fall-to-14-month-low-on-fed-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 00:41:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本零售贸易商削减对墨西哥比索的看涨押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/japan-retail-traders-slash-bullish-bets-on-mexican-peso</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本个人投资者将墨西哥比索兑日元的看涨押注降至今年最低水平，这一迹象表明国内加息可能降低他们对海外高收益资产的兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/japan-retail-traders-slash-bullish-bets-on-mexican-peso</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 00:39:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Energy Absolute 任命新首席执行官，将寻求更多时间偿还债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/energy-absolute-names-new-ceo-will-seek-more-time-to-pay-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国可再生能源公司 Energy Absolute Pcl 因涉嫌欺诈调查而市值暴跌，该公司任命了一位新首席执行官，并表示计划与债券持有人会面，寻求更多时间偿还债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/energy-absolute-names-new-ceo-will-seek-more-time-to-pay-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 00:35:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行政策变动震动市场，日本股市创 2020 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/japan-s-topix-enters-correction-as-yen-strength-hits-exporters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市出现 2020 年以来最大跌幅，基准东证指数较 7 月份高点下跌逾 10%，受紧缩货币政策影响，日本这个全球表现最好的市场之一陷入动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/japan-s-topix-enters-correction-as-yen-strength-hits-exporters</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 00:07:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
